    {
      "id": "firstJobSuccess2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "dialogue": {
        "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
        "text": "You've gotten much stronger now. Plus every single one of your inventories have added slots. A whole row, to be exact. Go see for it yourself. I just gave you a little bit of #bSP#k. When you open up the #bSkill#k menu on the lower left corner of the screen, there are skills you can learn by using SP's. One warning, though: You can't raise it all together all at once. There are also skills you can acquire only after having learned a couple of skills first.",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Previous",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess1"
          },
          {
            "text": "Next",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Exit",
            "nextState": null
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "firstJobSuccess3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "dialogue": {
        "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
        "text": "But remember, skills aren't everything. Your stats should support your skills as a Magician, also. Magicians use INT as their main stat, and LUK as their secondary stat. If raising stats is difficult, just use #bAuto-Assign#k",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Previous",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess2"
          },
          {
            "text": "Next",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess4"
          },
          {
            "text": "Exit",
            "nextState": null
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "firstJobSuccess4",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "dialogue": {
        "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
        "text": "Now, one more word of warning to you. If you fail in battle from this point on, you will lose a portion of your total EXP. Be extra mindful of this, since you have less HP than most.",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Previous",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Next",
            "nextState": "firstJobSuccess5"
          },
