    {
      "id": "secondJobComplete1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "dialogue": {
        "dialogueType": "sendNext",
        "text": "Alright, you're the {context.jobName} from here on out. Mages and wizards are the intelligent bunch with incredible magical prowess, able to pierce the mind and the psychological structure of the monsters with ease... please train yourself each and everyday. I'll help you become even stronger than you already are.",
